      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLEAR CODE (5) won by 9 lengths last start at this track 520m in a useful 29.78. In form and looks the one to beat again. HARA'S GREGOR (2) continues to build a strong record, the latest jumping cleanly to lead all the way (30.10) at this track in Maiden over 520m. Superior out of the boxes and will be in the firing line early. Speedy beginner who should be prominent early on from an inside box. Can make it back-to-back wins. SHULTZ UNLEASHED (3) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 3.5 lengths back in second (30.34) at this track in a Maiden over 520m. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Expecting another good run. HARA'S ARYA (1) missed the placings here on debut but looks an improver who can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
